## Key Edge Cases

| Input | Result | Notes |
|-------|--------|-------|
| `"My Project"` | `projectSlug: "my-project"` | Space→dash + lowercase |
| `"My Org/My Project"` | `org: "my-org", project: "my-project"` | Both parts normalized |
| `"My  Project"` | `projectSlug: "my-project"` | Consecutive dashes collapsed |
| `"My_Project Name"` | `projectSlug: "my-project-name"` | Both underscore + space, reason: "both" |
| `"org/ My Project"` | `project: "my-project"` | Leading dash from space trimmed |
| `"CLI-G5\n"` | `projectSlug: "cli", suffix: "G5"` | Trimmed before parsing |
| `"  \n  "` | ValidationError: empty | Empty after trim throws |
| `"my_project"` | `projectSlug: "my-project"` | Existing behavior preserved, NOT lowercased |
| `"12345 6789"` (issue ID) | ValidationError | Internal space in issue ID still rejected (no normalization, only trim) |

